<div class="alterMobile">
  <Header
    [title]="headerTitle"
    (onVoted)="back()">
    >
  </Header>
  <div class="grayBgBar mt80Rem"></div>
  <div class="alterMobileForm WrapB">
    <div class="formIpt">
      <div class="title">新手机号码</div>
      <input class="input" placeholder="请输入新手机号码" name="originMobile" [(ngModel)]="para.mobile" type="number">
    </div>

    <div class="formIpt">
      <div class="title">图片验证码</div>
      <input class="input" [(ngModel)]="para.captchaValue" name="originMobile" type="text">
      <div feedButton class="rightOpr" (click)="getCaptcha()">
        <img [src]="codeUrl" style="width: 100%;height: 1.1425rem !important;" src="../../../../assets/images/prt_list_img.png" alt="">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="formIpt">
      <div class="title">短信验证码</div>
      <input class="input" [(ngModel)]="para.code" name="originMobile" name="verCode" type="text">
      <div feedButton class="rightOpr getVerCode"  (click)="getBindMobileMsg()" [ngClass]="{disable:!canGetVcode}">
        {{getCodeText}}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div feedButton class="nextStepBtn btn" (click)="bindMobile()">完成</div>
  </div>
  <div class="tipsArea bgGreen">
    <p>温馨提示</p>
    <p>1、登录密码不能和您的支付密码一致</p>
    <p>2、请勿将支付密码告诉他人</p>
    <p>3、请勿在其他平台、软件中输入支付密码</p>
  </div>
</div>
